<lb ed="I" n="0178a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 71</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0178a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>陳神忻七十二人等造石室記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0179a" xml:id="I01.0071.0179a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0179a0101">當陽像主衛買興
<lb ed="I" n="0179a02"/>香火主清信士女衛姿容
<lb ed="I" n="0179a03"/>唯大齊皇建二年歲次<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179001" n="0179001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179001" n="0179001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179001" n="0179001"/>辛<anchor xml:id="end0179001"/>巳五月
<lb ed="I" n="0179a04"/>丙午<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179002" n="0179002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179002" n="0179002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179002" n="0179002"/>朔<anchor xml:id="end0179002"/>廿五日庚午。并州樂平郡
<lb ed="I" n="0179a05"/>石艾縣安鹿交村邑義陳神忻。合
<lb ed="I" n="0179a06"/>□邑子七十二人<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179003" n="0179003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179003" n="0179003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179003" n="0179003"/>等<anchor xml:id="end0179003"/>。敬造石室一
<lb ed="I" n="0179a07"/>區。今得成<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179004" n="0179004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179004" n="0179004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179004" n="0179004"/>就<anchor xml:id="end0179004"/>。上為佛法興隆。又<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179005" n="0179005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179005" n="0179005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179005" n="0179005"/>願<anchor xml:id="end0179005"/>皇
<lb ed="I" n="0179a08"/>帝陛下。金輪應庭。聖祚凝遠。群遼
<lb ed="I" n="0179a09"/>宰守。貢謁以時。國土安寧。兵駕不
<lb ed="I" n="0179a10"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179006" n="0179006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179006" n="0179006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179006" n="0179006"/>起<anchor xml:id="end0179006"/>。五<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179007" n="0179007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179007" n="0179007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179007" n="0179007"/>穀<anchor xml:id="end0179007"/>熟成。人民安樂。下為七世
<lb ed="I" n="0179a11"/>先亡。見存師僧父母。因緣眷。蠢動
<lb ed="I" n="0179a12"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179008" n="0179008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179008" n="0179008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179008" n="0179008"/>眾<anchor xml:id="end0179008"/>生。有形之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179009" n="0179009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179009" n="0179009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179009" n="0179009"/>類<anchor xml:id="end0179009"/>。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179010" n="0179010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179010" n="0179010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179010" n="0179010"/>越<anchor xml:id="end0179010"/>三途之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179011" n="0179011"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179011" n="0179011"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179011" n="0179011"/>苦<anchor xml:id="end0179011"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179012" n="0179012"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179012" n="0179012"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179012" n="0179012"/>難<anchor xml:id="end0179012"/>。居
<lb ed="I" n="0179a13"/>登政覺。
<lb ed="I" n="0179a14"/>八<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179013" n="0179013"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179013" n="0179013"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179013" n="0179013"/>關<anchor xml:id="end0179013"/>齋主呂<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">和</unclear>　　　　　進
<lb ed="I" n="0179a15"/>齋主扳授恒州
<lb ed="I" n="0179a16"/>齋主藉<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0179014" n="0179014"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0179014" n="0179014"/><anchor xml:id="beg0179014" n="0179014"/>雙<anchor xml:id="end0179014"/>憐
<lb ed="I" n="0179a17"/>齋主王保愛
<lb ed="I" n="0179a18"/>齋主施<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>雙<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>任
<lb ed="I" n="0179a19"/>齋主暢景略　齋主暢又為父母
<lb ed="I" n="0179a20"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a21"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a22"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a23"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179a24"/>輪王主張德仁
<lb ed="I" n="0179a25"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">衝</unclear>天王主張黑仁</p></cb:div></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0179b" xml:id="I01.0071.0179b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0179b00"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陰</head><cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0179b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0179b0101">邑主陳神忻邑子衛萇洛邑子衛強珍
<lb ed="I" n="0179b02"/>邑子衛天勝邑子樂和仁邑子衛高□
<lb ed="I" n="0179b03"/>邑子王領悅邑子王牛山邑子王阿□
<lb ed="I" n="0179b04"/>邑子楊阿安邑子韓智悅邑子張惡仁
<lb ed="I" n="0179b05"/>邑子衛伯達邑子衛始儁邑子衛阿陽
<lb ed="I" n="0179b06"/>邑子衛北陽邑子王阿標邑子郭張□
<lb ed="I" n="0179b07"/>邑子王曇信邑子衛宗和邑子衛元伯
<lb ed="I" n="0179b08"/>邑子張元伯邑子衛□□邑子王遵勝
<lb ed="I" n="0179b09"/>邑子侯阿顯邑子衛婆仁邑子張進国
<lb ed="I" n="0179b10"/>邑子衛阿義邑子衛阿季邑子陳阿慧
<lb ed="I" n="0179b11"/>邑子衛董定邑子張相如邑子張黑仁
<lb ed="I" n="0179b12"/>邑子衛顯和邑子張法山邑子張万保
<lb ed="I" n="0179b13"/>邑子郭阿統邑子張阿斥邑子郭進伯
<lb ed="I" n="0179b14"/>邑子衛元穆邑子衛阿斛邑子張阿貴
<lb ed="I" n="0179b15"/>邑子衛祖欣邑子衛宣德邑子郭神龜
<lb ed="I" n="0179b16"/>邑子王貴遵邑子王長孫邑子張阿奴
<lb ed="I" n="0179b17"/>邑子張轉勝邑子李迴族邑子王崇先
<lb ed="I" n="0179b18"/>邑子張阿渥邑子楮元勝邑子衛阿<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">侯</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0179b19"/>邑子李<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">貴</unclear>勝邑子李小勝邑子尹姿羅
<lb ed="I" n="0179b20"/>邑子藉顯貴邑子衛舍欣邑子衛令欣
<lb ed="I" n="0179b21"/>邑子衛文貴邑子張<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">永</unclear>賓邑子李思祖
<lb ed="I" n="0179b22"/>邑子張強族邑子張顯和邑子張蘭得
<lb ed="I" n="0179b23"/>上為亡父。見存阿婆。先亡
<lb ed="I" n="0179b24"/>兄。因緣眷屬。一時成佛。
<lb ed="I" n="0179b25"/>當陽像主張強族</p></cb:div></cb:div>
</body>
